&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-sourcepos=&quot;22:1-22:22&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vagas disponíveis:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-sourcepos=&quot;24:1-25:0&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-sourcepos=&quot;24:1-25:0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;8 vagas&lt;/strong&gt; para universidades da Argentina, Bolívia, Paraguai e Uruguai.&lt;/li&gt;
