&lt;p data-sourcepos=&quot;47:1-47:21&quot;&gt;Recomendamos que todos os estudantes leiam o edital completo antes de se inscrever.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Acesse o Edital completo &lt;a href=&quot;https://reinter2.furg.br/images/EDITAL_ESCALA_graduao_2024-2.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;clicando aqui.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-sourcepos=&quot;49:1-49:42&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://reinter2.furg.br/images/ANEXO_1_Escala_2024-2.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;ANEXO 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-sourcepos=&quot;49:1-49:42&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/document/d/1mccad5EBjoEjTVX4eXg3pX9uQC9OgKyH/edit?usp=sharing&amp;amp;ouid=102606015766162191884&amp;amp;rtpof=true&amp;amp;sd=true&quot;&gt;Contrato de Estudos&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Eventuais dúvidas do processo podem ser retiradas através do e-mail: &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:reinter.mobilidade@furg.br&quot;&gt;reinter.mobilidade@furg.br&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-sourcepos=&quot;52:1-52:77&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Não perca essa oportunidade de realizar um intercâmbio na América Latina!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
